\pard{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf2\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sl276\slmult1\cf1\f0\fs26 Set in the Empire of Aurumlux, a nation under perpetual rule of the Kilbor family, who has ruled the land since the capital city of Aurumlux was first settled by Lucius Kilbor in the 5th Era\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}You are the lone child in a family of vagrants making your way from the Sapphire Coast to find employment in the mainland.\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}You are abruptly awakened during your first night in Aurumlux to discover your family being forcefully taken by numerous cloaked figures. They do not notice you. You must discover the truth behind what happened. \par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}Starting from nothing, you will do whatever it takes to recover your family before it is too late.\par

