\cf0 Stone Cold Dead: \cf1 Kari the Marketeer keeps receiving boxes of dead mice delivered to her public market in the quiet of night, and she doesn't know who is doing it! She needs you to find out what is going on. As Ulvor explores Mireworth, he will eventually encounter a small Goblin encampment to the southeast of the Market, off in the forest in the direction of Nylar. Fight through the small Goblin encampment to speak with the Goblin commando Rado, who will tell you \highlight3 (after you do a quest for him?)\highlight0  that he has been trying to find a way to confuse the Market lady's boxes, so that one night he can swap out a box of rare fabrics and gemstones with a box of similarly-weighted dead mice, leftover food from the Goblin camp.\par

